                                <p>To provide the type of observation in coded form.</p>
                                <p>In this context, the type of observation is an observation of previous NHS contact information.</p>
                                <p>The Coded with Code System datatype flavour is used to carry this information as follows:</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>The <em>code</em>attribute will contain value "17" (Previous NHS contact) from the list of codes in the <u>DemographicObservationType</u>vocabulary;</li>
                                    <li>The <em>codeSystem</em>attribute will contain the OID referenced in the <u>DemographicObservationType</u>vocabulary.</li>
